To: FEMA Center For Domestic Preparedness:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

Hello, 
Can you please confirm if this SID number and ID card was issued and in who's name it was issued to? 
Federal Emergency Management Agency > Center for Domestic Preparedness: Student Identification Number: 0000866833


This request is not being made for commercial purposes.

There should be no fees associated with this request but in the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would fulfill my request and attach an invoice. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment of a written letter.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Mason C. Turner
TurnerMason@gmail.com
